Class SwapVariableUsage

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
java.util.AbstractList<StackEntry>
de.unisb.cs.st.javaslicer.instructionSimulation.SwapVariableUsage
All Implemented Interfaces:
DynamicInformation, Iterable<StackEntry>, Collection<StackEntry>, List<StackEntry>, RandomAccess
public class SwapVariableUsage
extends AbstractList<StackEntry>
implements DynamicInformation, RandomAccess
Object for the variable usages of a SWAP instruction, at the same time the list of used variables of the SWAP instruction (which is the same as the defined variables).
Author:
Clemens Hammacher
